(1) Run the Python scripts in "1-Transformation.ipynb".
    The raw data will be transformed into the following formats.

        '0' --> JSON
        '1' --> XML
        '2' --> CSV
        '3' --> CSV (*To be transformed to AVRO)
        '4' --> CSV (*To be transformed to RCFILE)
        '5' --> PARQUET

(2) Run the Hive script "2-TransformationInHive.sh".

(3) Use the following files in the modelling pipeline.

        JSON    : JSON/* (one file = one record)
        XML     : XML/* (one file = one record)
        CSV     : CSV/emails-2.csv
        AVRO    : AVRO/emails-3.avro
        RCFILE  : RCFILE/emails-4.rcfile
        PARQUET : PARQUET/emails-5.parquet
